      "id": "line-000",
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 8.94,
      "text": "This is a Libervox recording. All Libervox recordings are in the public domain. For more",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-001",
      "start": 8.94,
      "end": 14.18,
      "text": "information or to volunteer, please visit Libervox.org.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-002",
      "start": 16.24,
      "end": 20.82,
      "text": "ESOP's Fables. The She-Gotes and their Beards.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 22.84,
      "end": 30.82,
      "text": "Jupyter granted Beards to the She-Gotes at their own request, much to the disgust of the He-Gotes,",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 31.26,
      "end": 39.98,
      "text": "who considered this to be an unwarranted invasion of their rights and dignities. So they sent a",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 39.98,
      "end": 48.08,
      "text": "deputation to him to protest against his action. He, however, advised them not to raise any objections.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 49.44,
      "end": 58.24,
      "text": "What's in a tuft of hair, said he? Let them have it if they want it. They can never be a match for you in strength.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 59.6,
      "end": 66.2,
      "text": "The end of the She-Gotes and their Beards. Red by Abraham.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
